# Tailscale Authentication Key
# Get your auth key from: https://login.tailscale.com/admin/settings/keys
#
# IMPORTANT: Use a reusable key with appropriate tags
# Recommended settings when creating the key:
#   - Reusable: Yes
#   - Ephemeral: No (so it persists across restarts)
#   - Tags: iris (or create a custom tag)
#   - Expiration: 90 days (or longer)
#
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual key

TS_AUTHKEY=